{"tid":146054,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"想搵一首國語歌","createTime":"2017-03-06T17:17:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-06T18:59:07.000Z","uid":33749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e975dad1138acca1bd4da3dda43b777eb0f7ca3c","tid":146054,"uid":33749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T17:17:38.000Z","msg":"以前細個聽過<br />\n尋晚出街無意中又聽到<br />\n歌詞淨係記得一句<br />\n你真是弱智弱智弱智啦啦喇<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06ce687a09d82fe596455fdd9a764da0299c09d4","tid":146054,"uid":33749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T17:21:24.000Z","msg":"推下"},{"pid":"14554f16e6ea32b0ed56845c53aa707ea299fde4","tid":146054,"uid":61678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T17:24:39.000Z","msg":"郭富城既弱"},{"pid":"e356578b15db616438efecbd8aa6ac3703e971b7","tid":146054,"uid":33749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T17:31:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>郭富城既弱</blockquote><br />\n郭富城嘅弱 <br />\n<br />\n打牌輸左八番　排茶樓又冇檯　 <br />\n好想沖廁但冇水夠悲哀　 <br />\n今朝生左炸鰓　屎坑都坐爛蓋 <br />\n還有沒有未來？ <br />\n<br />\n比貓爪傷個咀　搽神油又冇女 <br />\n想跟風去食素得塊火腿 <br />\n周身得返兩蚊 飲冰水會淥親　 <br />\n褲襠有乳酸菌 <br />\n<br />\n強人是你　人生好乏味 <br />\n同自己冇得比　比起你我乜野都難做到 <br />\n強人是你　能讓我好妒忌 <br />\n原諒我 對不起 我就黎死　 <br />\n人活著是一督屁 <br />\n<br />\n神油搽十次 唔抬頭又試 <br />\n再試兩試發生怪事 <br />\n忙垂頭望下 <br />\n原來頭部變紫 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://h.saren.me/jRI3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fh.saren.me%2FjRI3&d=IX2zbuQlYI18gOdM245y9%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=fb5ae0eb\" target=\"_blank\">http://h.saren.me/jRI3</a>"},{"pid":"172c2c8fb1e897a08406728ca51261fb2ab61a62","tid":146054,"uid":33749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T17:37:07.000Z","msg":"推下"},{"pid":"9854abf3560d331a50a9c735f459a009dc05c33d","tid":146054,"uid":33749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"